result.title: [552B. Vanya and Books] Wrong output when run on CodeForces compiler on Test 6!
result.content:
Dear all,

When I submit the source code, the system told that "Wrong answer on test 6". The output from CodeForces compiler gave "5888895" and expected answer is "5888896". When I check again from www.IDEONE.com the output is "5888896". I also checked from http://cpp.sh/ and the output is "5888896" too.

I have tested very carefully on the source code for this case but the output from CodeForces compiler always is "5888895". I have no idea about this. Hope someone can help me.

My submission on CodeForces: http://codeforces.com/contest/552/submission/11704744

And from IDEONE: https://ideone.com/xX0bYC

Thanks and best regards!
